isis.stitle: TSI 96-12-19 - Performance Specifications for 1994, 1995 and 1996 T 444E Engine Applications

subjectgroup.subject: Performance Specifications for 1994, 1995 and 1996 T 444E Engine Applications

geninfo.para: Engine Performance Specifications are being released to service for the T 444E engine applications listed below.

note.para: Refer to the emission label on the engine to correctly identify the Engine Model Year and Horsepower Rating (indicated by punched hole).
